Arthur,<br>
     There is a very good teacher where my sons went to high school, who is a Vietnam Vet.  A high profile guy, he keeps quiet about his time in service.  If asked, he says that its' a part of his life that's over and done with, and that he's someone else now...End of topic!<br>
     Whatever he learned in that time is evidently to painful or uncomfortable to be shared lest it claim him again.  A shame really.  His students would probably benefit from the insights of the man he has become on what he went through.  Many will learn the hard way.
